# Assets Directory

This directory contains static assets for the OneLink application.

## Structure

- `images/` - Image files (logos, icons, backgrounds)
- `fonts/` - Custom font files
- `icons/` - SVG icons

## Usage

Import assets in your components:

```jsx
import logo from '@/assets/images/logo.svg'

function Component() {
  return <img src={logo} alt="Logo" />
}